Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.88,0:33:16.60,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,そんな 大それたことじゃないけどさ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.60,0:33:19.64,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,ただ
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.16,0:33:23.92,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,もし 俺に できるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.08,0:33:27.44,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,苦しんでる村や
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.42,0:33:31.34,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,お春ちゃんみたいな人たちを
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.02,0:33:33.82,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,助けたい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.54,0:33:37.48,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,そう 思っただけ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.38,0:33:43.52,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,だから もう…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.42,0:33:49.36,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,逃げないよ｡
