Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.82,0:34:24.46,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,ホント いいやつだな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.30,0:34:26.86,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,いえ｡
