Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.38,0:39:43.08,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,あそこだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.14,0:39:52.36,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,狙うは
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.70,0:39:55.56,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,今川 義元 ただ 一人｡
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.54,0:39:59.12,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,行くぞ！
